  m_text: "While everyone\u2019s posting beach photos, Alex scrolls through the feed
    alone. The room is quiet, but the wallet\u2019s a bit heavier. A small sigh escapes
    \u2014 \u201CNext time, siguro.\u201D Still, the thought of that growing savings
    brings calm comfort"
