  m_text: "The morning rush hums outside as Alex squeezes into the jeepney, bag snug
    on the lap. Every peso saved means packed lunches and long rides \u2014 but also
    family dinners with \u201CIngat ha.\u201D The days may be tiring, but home sure
    are a commute away"
